OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,FVideo footage shows the trapped
OL,7,Fvillagers being found alive after
OL,8,Fspending a week inside the cave
OL,10,FFive of the seven people trapped in a
OL,11,Fflooded cave in Laos have been found
OL,12,Falive by rescuers.
OL,14,FThey were located by specialist cave
OL,15,Fdivers on Wednesday but remain trapped
OL,16,Fin an underground cavern in Laos'
OL,17,Fcentral Xaisomboun province, as
OL,18,Frescuers continue searching for the
OL,19,Ftwo remaining missing people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
