OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779922985
OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,F"5 people have been found safe. The
OL,7,Fsearch continues for the remaining 2,"
OL,8,FThai rescue diver Kengkad Bongkawong
OL,9,Fwrote on Facebook.
OL,11,FA Laotian rescue group, Rescue
OL,12,FVolunteer for People, said that the
OL,13,Ffive found were "alive and all safe".
OL,15,FFinnish diver Mikko Paasi, who is a
OL,16,Fpart of the rescue operation, wrote on
OL,17,FInstagram: "The task so far has been
OL,18,Ffar from easy and everybody involved
OL,19,Fhas done amazing work."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
