CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779922985
OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,FHowever, he added it was "only a brief
OL,7,Frelief," as the survivors are still
OL,8,Fstuck in the cavern for now.
OL,10,F"All healthy and in good spirits, but
OL,11,Fthe extraction is still ahead and it
OL,12,Fain't going to be easy," he said.
OL,14,FThe task for him and another diver
OL,15,Fwould now be to "dive straight back"
OL,16,Fand bring the residents more supplies
OL,17,Fso that they can regain their strength
OL,18,Fto prepare for the journey out, he
OL,19,Fsaid.
