OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,FA video filmed by Mikko Paasi showed
OL,7,Frescuers asking the residents for
OL,8,Ftheir names and whether they were
OL,9,Fsuffering from illness.
OL,11,FThe group said they were not sick, but
OL,12,Ffelt weak and extremely hungry.
OL,14,FThose trapped will undergo medical
OL,15,Fassessments and be given liquid and
OL,16,Fgel food before a plan is made to
OL,17,Fbring them out safely, local
OL,18,Fauthorities said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
