OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe rescue operation is expected to be
OL,12,Fdifficult.
OL,14,FAccording to the Metta Tham Kalasin
OL,15,FCommand and Control Centre, divers had
OL,16,Fto navigate a 340-metre tunnel to
OL,17,Freach the group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
