OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779922985
OL,3,CFive of seven people trapped in Laos
OL,4,Ccave found alive, rescuers say
OL,6,FSome sections of the flooded cave are
OL,7,Fbelieved to be just 23 inches wide,
OL,8,Fforcing at least one rescuer to remove
OL,9,Fequipment to squeeze through.
OL,11,FGoPro footage showed rescuers reaching
OL,12,Ffive of the seven trapped people,
OL,13,Freassuring them by saying, "don't cry,
OL,14,Fdon't cry."
OL,16,FRescuers said more than 100 people are
OL,17,Finvolved in the rescue effort,
OL,18,Fincluding divers who took part in the
OL,19,F2018 rescue of a youth football team
OL,20,Ffrom a cave in Thailand.
